'''2013年錫斯坦－俾路支斯坦省地震'''，发生于伊朗當地時間2013年4月16日15时14分（[[UTC+4:30|UTC+4:30]]），震央位于[[伊朗|伊朗]]和[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]边境[[錫斯坦－俾路支斯坦省|錫斯坦－俾路支斯坦省]][[薩拉萬|薩拉萬市]]和[[哈什_(伊朗)|哈什市]]之间，[[矩震級|矩震級]]7.8。<ref name="bbc Major">{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22168202 |title=BBC News — Major earthquake strikes south-east Iran |publisher=Bbc.co.uk |date=1970-01-01 |accessdate=2013-04-16 |archive-date=2020-11-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123181320/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-22168202 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/usb000g7x7.php#details |title=Magnitude 7.8 – IRAN-PAKISTAN BORDER REGION |publisher=Earthquake.usgs.gov |date= |accessdate=2013-04-16 |archive-date=2013-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130419210946/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/earthquakes/recenteqsww/Quakes/usb000g7x7.php#details |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/quake-iran-pakistan-india-935/ |title=Hundreds feared dead in 7.8 Iran earthquake, also felt in New Delhi, Gulf States — RT News |publisher=Rt.com |date=2013-04-10 |accessdate=2013-04-16 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126103642/https://www.rt.com/news/quake-iran-pakistan-india-935/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2013/04/16/world/meast/iran-pakistan-earthquake/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |title=Reports: Dozens feared dead after strong quake rocks Iran, Pakistan — CNN.com |publisher=Edition.cnn.com |date=2001-09-11 |accessdate=2013-04-16 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118120201/http://edition.cnn.com/2013/04/16/world/meast/iran-pakistan-earthquake/index.html?hpt=hp_t1 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/04/2013416111232927572.html |title=Major quake jolts southeastern Iran — Central & South Asia |publisher=Al Jazeera English |date=2011-10-04 |accessdate=2013-04-16 |archive-date=2020-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906211531/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia/2013/04/2013416111232927572.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://live.reuters.com/Event/Iran_Earthquake |title=Iran Earthquake | Liveblog live blogging | Reuters.com |publisher=Live.reuters.com |date=2009-02-09 |accessdate=2013-04-16 |archive-date=2019-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912001037/http://live.reuters.com/Event/Iran_Earthquake?Page=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>持续约25秒。<ref name="bbc Major"/>

此地震是伊朗在过去40年来最强烈的地震。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/04/16/298564/75magnitude-quake-kills-40-in-se-iran/|title=Magnitude 7.5 quake jolts Sistan-Baluchestan in SE Iran, kills 40|date=2013-04-16|accessdate=2013-04-16|archive-date=2013-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130419011240/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2013/04/16/298564/75magnitude-quake-kills-40-in-se-iran/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年4月9日伊朗西南部[[布什尔省|布什尔省]]刚刚发生[[2013年布什尔省地震|芮氏規模6.3的地震]]。<ref name="bbc Major"/>震中附近的Mashkel镇，85％左右的城市建筑被摧毁。<ref>{{cite news| url= http://www.3news.co.nz/Earthquake-flattens-Pakistan-town/tabid/417/articleID/294841/Default.aspx| work= 3 News NZ| title= Earthquake flattens Pakistan town| date= 2013-04-19| access-date= 2013-04-19| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130928060947/http://www.3news.co.nz/Earthquake-flattens-Pakistan-town/tabid/417/articleID/294841/Default.aspx| archive-date= 2013-09-28| dead-url= yes}}</ref>

==地震影响==
地震波及整个东部伊朗和巴基斯坦南部大部分地区，[[利雅得|利雅得]]、[[麦纳麦|麦纳麦]]、[[多哈|多哈]]、[[阿布扎比|阿布扎比]]、[[马斯喀特|马斯喀特]]和[[德里|德里]]均有震感。<ref name="bbc Major"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.muscatdaily.com/Archive/Oman/Massive-earthquake-hits-Iran-tremors-felt-across-Oman-region-26s4 |title=Massive earthquake hits Iran, tremors felt across Oman, region |access-date=2013-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420095848/http://www.muscatdaily.com/Archive/Oman/Massive-earthquake-hits-Iran-tremors-felt-across-Oman-region-26s4 |archive-date=2013-04-20 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.arabnews.com/news/448339 |title=Tremors create panic in EP, Riyadh |accessdate=2013-04-16 |archive-date=2020-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906205423/https://www.arabnews.com/news/448339 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==發生原因==
[[File:Arabian_tectonic_plate_overview_map.png|thumb]]

此次地震发生在[[阿拉伯板块|阿拉伯板块]]的密度大的大洋性质的地壳与[[欧亚板块|欧亚板块]]碰撞并俯冲到欧亚板块之下的{{link-en|马克兰隐没带|Makran Trench}}，从而形成的地震活跃、震源较深的“[[班尼奧夫帶|瓦班氏带]]”。震源深度80千米，属于中等深度地震。

==災情==
有消息称死亡40人，而伊朗政府随后否认有人死亡。<ref>{{cite web|last=News|first=Biharprabha|title=Major Earthquake strikes India, Pakistan, Iran, Sistan and Baluchestan|url=http://news.biharprabha.com/2013/04/major-earthquake-strikes-india-pakistan-and-iran/|accessdate=2013-04-16|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906210811/https://news.biharprabha.com/2013/04/major-earthquake-strikes-india-pakistan-and-iran/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=News|first=Earthquake Report|title=Iran officially denied the 40 deaths today|url=http://earthquake-report.com/2013/04/16/massive-earthquake-iran-pakistan-border-region-on-april-16-2013/|accessdate=2013-04-16|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906212503/https://earthquake-report.com/2013/04/16/massive-earthquake-iran-pakistan-border-region-on-april-16-2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而邻国巴基斯坦报告有34人死亡。<ref name="bbc Major"/>根据[[紅十字會與紅新月會國際聯合會|伊朗红新月会]]透露，该地区所有的通信都被切断，救援队已派出。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/hundreds-feared-killed-after-strong-78-magnitude-quake-hits-iran/article11253618/|title=Hundreds feared killed after strong 7.8-magnitude quake hits Iran|publisher=The Globe and Mail|date=2013-04-16|accessdate=2013-04-16|archive-date=2013-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130419044335/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/hundreds-feared-killed-after-strong-78-magnitude-quake-hits-iran/article11253618/|dead-url=no}}</ref>伊朗的许多建筑物被完全摧毁。<ref name="bbc Major"/>

===伤亡人数===
*{{flagicon|Iran}}伊朗至少有1人死亡，另有12人受伤。

*{{flagicon|Pakistan}}巴基斯坦至少有34人死亡，另有105人受伤。

